WITH movie_data AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS movie_id,
        t.title AS movie_title,
        t.production_year,
        ak.name AS actor_name,
        ak.imdb_index AS actor_imdb_index,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT kw.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
    FROM 
        aka_title t
    JOIN 
        cast_info c ON t.id = c.movie_id
    JOIN 
        aka_name ak ON c.person_id = ak.person_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        keyword kw ON mk.keyword_id = kw.id
    WHERE 
        t.production_year >= 2000
        AND ak.name IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY 
        t.id, t.title, t.production_year, ak.name, ak.imdb_index
),
company_info AS (
    SELECT 
        mc.movie_id,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT cn.name, ', ') AS company_names,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT ct.kind, ', ') AS company_types
    FROM 
        movie_companies mc
    JOIN 
        company_name cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id
    JOIN 
        company_type ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id
    GROUP BY 
        mc.movie_id
)
SELECT 
    md.movie_id,
    md.movie_title,
    md.production_year,
    md.actor_name,
    md.actor_imdb_index,
    ci.company_names,
    ci.company_types,
    md.keywords
FROM 
    movie_data md
JOIN 
    company_info ci ON md.movie_id = ci.movie_id
ORDER BY 
    md.production_year DESC, 
    md.movie_title ASC
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."MOVIE_ID", "t3"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t3"."ACTOR_NAME", "t3"."ACTOR_IMDB_INDEX", "t5"."COMPANY_NAMES", "t5"."COMPANY_TYPES", "t3"."KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_title"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", MIN("aka_title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", MIN("s1"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("s1"."imdb_index") AS "ACTOR_IMDB_INDEX", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "aka_title"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "aka_title"."production_year" >= 2000
GROUP BY "aka_title"."id", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year", "s1"."name", "s1"."imdb_index") AS "t3"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "movie_companies"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_name"."name", ', ') AS "COMPANY_NAMES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_type"."kind", ', ') AS "COMPANY_TYPES"
FROM "movie_companies"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
GROUP BY "movie_companies"."movie_id") AS "t5" ON "t3"."MOVIE_ID" = "t5"."MOVIE_ID"
ORDER BY "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE"
LIMIT 100
